profile:
Top Granite is a top-rated Montreal fabricator and installer of Marble, Quartz, Granite and other natural stone countertops.  We import our stones from all over the world, allowing you to choose from a large spectrum of stones and colors under one roof. We offer fabrication and installation of kitchens, bathrooms, stairs, elevators, entryways, hotel lobbies, shopping centers, and retail stores. 

For over 18 years; our combined experience within the stone industry and precision technology work hand-in-hand to bring our customers the top choice for hard stone in Montreal.
